STATE
v.
Corey F. MALDONADO 73P19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 9, 2019 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Brandy Cook, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Corey F. Maldonado, for Maldonado, Corey.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th of February 2019 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:
